name: "One Stroke Of My Pen" Album
description: SD Lyric, a 20 year old native Californian, is no stranger to the music industry. SD Lyric has spent countless hours in the studio, and on stage perfecting his skills; SD Lyric has performed at many of the local venues, as well as appeared on television talk shows such as “Ask Ari”. Currently attending a local California college, SD Lyric has displayed an exceptional ability to express himself through his lyrics. A product of Inglewood California, SD Lyric has been accused of having an “old soul”. This is evident in his selection of instrumentals; SD Lyric delivers a refreshing, different sound. Combining the street edge of today’s Hip Hop/Rap and the smooth two step sound of yesterday’s R&B, SD Lyric has managed to spin up some interesting ear candy for those of you who are listening for something different in an overly saturated music industry. By the way, it’s all clean.
